{"tid":1219552,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"同香港警察對立無意思","createTime":"2019-06-13T22:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T03:11:47.000Z","uid":93485,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f32075dee059d7841bac668ba07fd6a389ab4543","tid":1219552,"uid":93485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T22:50:26.000Z","msg":"【阿sir做野唔洗議員教？】 #我就教你睇警察通例<br />\n<br />\n今日中午一班警察瘋狂喺添馬公園check人身份證、搜身，其中絕大部份便衣都無配帶委任證。自稱「呢度我最大」嘅陳警司更口出狂言，話自己話佢係警察就係，無需符合《警察通例》第20章：「行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證」。陳警司唔熟書，就麻煩你再返學堂讀讀《警察通例》，事實上巿民提出要求，連軍裝警務人員都要出示委任證！<br />\n<br />\n而當時所有便衣都完全唔配合，問極都唔出示委任證，咁樣巿民點知呢班人有無冒警？亦無法以警員號碼投訴警察濫權。當然我就有呢位陳警司全名，已經即時向監警會作出投訴，你自己諗定點同board解釋啦！<br />\n<br />\n#陳警司話著件衫有個Police字就係<br />\n#相信佢都唔識有個意大利牌子叫POLICE <br />\n#著佢地牌子一定全部都係香港警察啦<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅 Andrew Wan合力夾攻 (y)<br />\n部份影片來源：香港電台視像新聞 RTHK VNEWS<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問下1:14分個冒警 <br />\n到底識唔識講廣東話 識唔識聽廣東話<br />\n<br />\n佢地係唔係香港警察 大家心中有數啦<br />\n敵人只有一個 </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/858421787553638/posts/2328165767245892?s=1560695038&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F858421787553638%2Fposts%2F2328165767245892%3Fs%3D1560695038%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=0a541878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/858421787553638/posts/2328165767245892?s=1560695038&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"d92c6845809ab7b97dca971b25838a5ba22c500d","tid":1219552,"uid":160605,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lm7ZDry.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLm7ZDry.jpg&h=7796f43d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n任達華表示：咁我係咪警察??"},{"pid":"e48d4a1826d611695c029a8052f6ce3d66a8cf1d","tid":1219552,"uid":93485,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:31:40.000Z","msg":"屌佢老無著住衫就係<br />\n我著住套cosplay去遊行啦"},{"pid":"700efafc337e6a82e6fba892d952e5509c0e422c","tid":1219552,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:36:38.000Z","msg":"屌你啦香港警察 殘暴行為比比皆是<br />\n香港警隊內部風氣早已經係咁既樣<br />\n14年早已睇到淪為政治風氣既警隊<br />\n仲有乜好講 黑警休班警屢屢犯案係咪又唔撚記得？<br />\n佢地做事咩態度又唔記得<br />\n平日見有事就唔想做急急close file<br />\n到有示威 一個二個急撚住開槍呀<br />\n香港公安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e976c728ae501aa5722ad0e179365208907e0f6","tid":1219552,"uid":169662,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:54:54.000Z","msg":"執著無用，歷史上無咩兵會倒戈，有良心好仔唔當差。"},{"pid":"6bd284a49785cc1da6cc8940bc074dadbc328e22","tid":1219552,"uid":92500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:43:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3e7e3e22f810f6cf5a8639d5113d0a5818a57a0","tid":1219552,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f361e1fb5933de8c38c87e3e50ed4808f7f0291","tid":1219552,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d92c6845809ab7b97dca971b25838a5ba22c500d","tid":1219552,"uid":160605,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lm7ZDry.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLm7ZDry.jpg&h=7796f43d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n任達華表示：咁我係咪警察??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:44:46.000Z","msg":"有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食卡士蘭啦，玩幾夜都得！"},{"pid":"08cada59a81792eec413b62e030ae4ffd2ff8476","tid":1219552,"uid":137986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:44:51.000Z","msg":"5.如何辨認警務人員之身份/警察委任證之真偽？<br />\n<br />\n警務人員在以下情況須出示警察委任證：<br />\n<br />\n便衣警務人員：在行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n軍裝警務人員：一般無須主動出示警察委任證，但如市民提出要求，他們亦須出示委任證，除非情況不容許，或要求不合理。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n當警務人員出示委任證，只須向提出要求的市民展示委任證，而不可將委任證轉交任何市民查閱。 如市民對警務人員身份或委任證存有懷疑，可立即聯絡就近警署 查詢。<br />\n　　警察委任證特徵如下：<br />\n<br />\n正面印有(包括中英文) ：　　<br />\n香港警察、　　<br />\n彩色警徽、　　<br />\n警務人員姓名、職級、僱員號碼、　　<br />\n相片，另有香港警察及HONG KONG POLICE 字眼的鐳射標記。　<br />\n<br />\n　<br />\n背面印有以下聲明：「本證持有人是經正式委任的香港警察，其相片及資料載於背面。」<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n(有關警察委任證之警訊片段&ndash; (冒警騙案))"},{"pid":"d5b0b15a6bd5574e4b44a2e872b31a929431156b","tid":1219552,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e48d4a1826d611695c029a8052f6ce3d66a8cf1d","tid":1219552,"uid":93485,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:31:40.000Z","msg":"屌佢老無著住衫就係<br />\n我著住套cosplay去遊行啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:45:20.000Z","msg":"夠疆你咪試囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c90606603ebd426e1e14e086bc7e00f0e04df7","tid":1219552,"uid":247237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d92c6845809ab7b97dca971b25838a5ba22c500d","tid":1219552,"uid":160605,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lm7ZDry.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLm7ZDry.jpg&h=7796f43d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n任達華表示：咁我係咪警察??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:45:42.000Z","msg":"對唔住，我係差人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7697f6458ad92bdccf09e54236d44a1981710b70","tid":1219552,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:11:47.000Z","msg":"[呼籲]發覺好多黑警del晒自己fb passing out啲相<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1220059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1220059</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}